    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a recently overhauled double-VANOS system to ensure optimal cam phasing. The chassis has been addressed with a subframe reinforcement kit, maintaining structural integrity under high lateral loads. Performance is supported by a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is exceptionally tight, delivering linear power through the individual throttle bodies up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A true driver\u2019s specimen for the technical purist.",
