    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 5 Series that perfectly balances performance and comfort. The exterior is finished in a crisp Alpine White that retains a high gloss, with only minimal, expected surface wear from careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of cracks, and the wood trim is pristine. All electronic features, from the navigation to the multi-zone climate control, operate exactly as they should. This car has been serviced strictly on schedule at authorized centers, with a full paper trail included. Most recently, it received a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming its solid mechanical health. With deep tire treads and a smooth-shifting transmission, this sedan is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
