    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our professional standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, this car offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning owner who prioritizes quality and long-term value.",
